    {
      "section_id": "para_43",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "An Act to provide for the application of certain provisions of the\nLoans (International Bank) Act 1958, to a guarantee by Malaysia of\na loan by the International Bank for Reconstruction and Development\nto  Malaysian  Industrial  Development  Finance  Limited  and  for\nmatters connected therewith.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_44",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "[Peninsular Malaysia—11 April 1963;\nSabah and Sarawak—8 October 1964]",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_45",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "BE IT ENACTED by the Seri Paduka Baginda Yang di-Pertuan\nAgong with the advice and consent of the Dewan Negara and Dewan\nRakyat in Parliament assembled, and by the authority of the same,\nas follows:",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_46",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Short title and application",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_47",
      "heading": "1. (1) This Act may be cited as the Loan Guarantee Act 1963.",
      "content": "1. (1) This Act may be cited as the Loan Guarantee Act 1963.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_48",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2) This Act shall apply throughout Malaysia.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_49",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Application of the Loans (International Bank) Act 1958",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_50",
      "heading": "2. (1) The following provisions of the Loans (International Bank)\nAct 1958 [Act 411], namely—",
      "content": "2. (1) The following provisions of the Loans (International Bank)\nAct 1958 [Act 411], namely—",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_51",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(a) section  7  (which  authorizes  the  Government  to  give\nguarantees and undertakings with respect to borrowings\nby  statutory  authorities  from  the  International  Bank  for\nReconstruction and Development); and",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_52",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(b) so far as they relate to guarantees and undertakings by the\nGovernment,  sections  11  and  12  (which  contain\nsupplementary provisions for the implementation, among\nother things, of any such guarantee or undertaking), save\nthat for the words “1950” in subsection 12(5), there shall\nbe substituted therefor the words “1960”,",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_53",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "6",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_54",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Laws of Malaysia",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_55",
      "heading": "ACT 412",
      "content": "ACT 412",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_56",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "shall  apply  in  relation  to  any  borrowing  from  that  Bank  by  the\ncompany called Malaysian Industrial Development Finance Limited\nas if the company were a statutory authority within the meaning of\nthat Act, and the borrowing were made under subsection 5(1) of the\nAct.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_57",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(2) If any sum is paid out of the Consolidated Fund in respect of\nany liability incurred by the Government by virtue of subsection (1),\nthe Minister shall as soon as possible after the end of each financial\nyear beginning with that in which the sum was paid and ending with\nthat in which all liability in respect thereof and any interest payable\nthereon is finally discharged by the company, lay before the Dewan\nRakyat a statement relating thereto.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_58",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "(3) The  said  paragraphs  12(2)(a)  and  (b)  (which  provides  for\nexemptions  from  taxation  and  from  exchange  control)  shall  also\napply  in  relation  to  any  agreement  concluded,  whether  before  or\nafter the passing of this Act, with the Bank by the company, with the\napproval  of  the  Government,  in  respect  of  any  borrowing  by  the\ncompany  from  the  Bank,  and  to  any  bond,  promissory  note  or\ninstrument issued by the company pursuant to any such agreement,\nas they apply to the agreements and instruments there mentioned.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_59",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Ratification of Agreement of Guarantee",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_60",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "3. The agreement of guarantee heretofore concluded between the\nGovernment in the name of the Federation of Malaysia and the Bank\nis hereby ratified and validated in all respects and shall have effect\nfor all purposes as if this Act had been in force on such date and the\nsaid agreement had been duly concluded and executed in exercise of\nthe powers conferred by or under this Act.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_61",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "Extension to other companies",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
    {
      "section_id": "para_62",
      "heading": "",
      "content": "If a resolution be passed by the Dewan Rakyat that section 2 of\n4.\nthis Act shall apply to any company, as they apply to the Malaysian\nIndustrial Development Finance Limited, then the Minister may, by\nOrder to be published in the Gazette, declare that the said provision\nshall apply to that company.",
      "section_number": null,
      "subsection": null,
      "page_number": null,
      "element_type": "text"
    },
